== Aho biherereye ==
Urugomero ruherereye k'[[umugezi wa Nyabarongo]], hafi y'umudugudu wa ''Mushishiro'', [[Akarere ka Muhanga]], mu Ntara y'Amajyepfo . <ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2020/02/rwanda-china-to-sign-financing-deal-for-nyabarongo-power-project/</ref>harimo 75 kilometres (47 mi), kumuhanda, mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba bwa [[Kigali]], [[Umurwa|umurwa mukuru]] mu Rwanda. <ref>http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Kigali%20(Kigali)%20&toplace=Mushishiro%20(Gitarama)&fromlat=-1.9536111&tolat=-2.3&fromlng=30.0605556&tolng=29.65</ref> Mushishiro iri hafi 35 kilometres (22 mi), kumuhanda, mumajyepfo yicyicaro cyintara y'amajyepfo . <ref>http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Gitarama%20(Gitarama)%20&toplace=Mushishiro%20(Gitarama)&fromlat=-2.0744444&tolat=-2.3&fromlng=29.7566667&tolng=29.65</ref>

== Incamake ==
Urugomero rwa Nyabarongo I ni urugomero rw'amashanyarazi mu Rwanda, rwuzuye mu Kwakira 2014, rufite itariki yo gutangizwa mu Gushyingo 2014. Ku kigereranyo cya miliyoni 110 US $, hateganijwe kwishyiriraho ubushobozi bwa MW 28. Uyu mushinga urimo urugomero, rufite igishushanyo mbonera cy’uruzi, hakurya y'Uruzi i Mwogo, imwe mu masoko [[Umugezi wa Nyabarongo|y'uruzi rwa Nyabarongo]] . Uyu mushinga, wakozwe na '''Angelique International Limited''' & Bharat Heavy Electricals Limited yo mu [[Ubuhinde|Buhinde]], n’umushinga munini w'amashanyarazi mu [[Rwanda]], kugeza ubu.  Naresh Kapoor Sr.,  ni Umuyobozi mukuru ushinzwe umushinga washyizweho na Angelique International Limited yo mu [[Ubuhinde|Buhinde]] .  Bimwe mubikorwa byubwubatsi byanasezeranye nisosiyete yo muri Ositaraliya Snowy Mountains Engineering Corporation (SMEC).  Ibyo bice byombi byahujwe na gride yu Rwanda ku ya 27 Ukwakira 2014 na 30 Ukwakira 2014. Guverinoma y'u Rwanda yahaye rwiyemezamirimo igihe ntarengwa mu Kwakira 2014.  urugomero rw’amashanyarazi rwararangiye ishyikirizwa abakiriya ku ya 28 Ugushyingo 2014. Yafunguwe ku mugaragaro na perezida w'u Rwanda ku ya 5 Werurwe 2015. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/nyabarongo-hydro-power-plant-cost-214-million</ref><ref>https://www.eia.nl/documenten/00000508.pdf</ref><ref>https://www.igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/muhanga-abaturiye-urugomero-rwa-nyabarongo-batagerwaho-n-amashanyarazi-baremwe</ref><ref>http://www.rba.co.rw/minisitiri-musoni-yasuye-urugomero</ref>

